ight and then amend them upon seeing the true head, left-to-right processing and immediatehead parsing might be joined.
    Note that one of the cases where this might be worrisome, early words in a base noun-phrase could be conditioned upon a head which comes several words later, has been made significantly less problematic by our revised definition of heads inside noun-phrases.
    We believe that other such situations can be brought into line as well, thus again taming the search problem.
    However, this too is a topic for future research.
  

